---
alwaysApply: true
---

Read the README.md file for more information.

Use nuxt-ui mvp to work with ui/ux related functionality.

Components in UI layer, where ui libs componetns are applyed are used like boundery between ui/ux libs and the app.

Don't use pure nuxt-ui components, use the components in the UI layer.

When component business logic gets thick, move it into a composable and keep the component focused on props/emits wiring and presentation.

All event handler function names should start with `on` (for example: `onSubmit`, `onClick`).

